P_2
T(1) = \int_0^x 1\ dt = x
T(t) = \int_0^x t\ dt = \frac{x^2}{2}
[T] = \begin{pmatrix}0 & 0 \\ 1 & 0 \\ 0 & \frac{1}{2}\end{pmatrix}
